        <section id="roots">
            <h2>The Beginning</h2>
            <p>Every meaningful growth begins in darkness, in the quiet depths where we retreat to nurture our strength.</p>
            <p>Like seeds beneath the soil, we gather resources, prepare, and wait for the right moment to push upward. This space of apparent stillness is where transformation truly begins.</p>
            <p>The internal work done in these moments—reflection, healing, learning—forms the foundation that supports all future expansion.</p>
        </section>
        
        <figure id="trunk" class="responsive">
